ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有個帖都屌緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想講莫文蔚拎至尊歌實至名歸，不服來辯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349604</a><br />\n<br />\n佢同林憶蓮我都唔明點解要咁樣奶法，為乜啫，又唔係冇錢。佢嗰代基本上都係返大陸搵食多，其實真係好閒，係唔知點解佢兩個又唔係大陸人要奶到做埋成輯節目啫，到今日我都唔明白。尤其是林，唉佢一出新碟我真係loop到爛，真係曾經搞到我都好撚激心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7590110d56208fcd3495e7ca169d4ebff1286623","tid":2350192,"uid":294343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1055f33698ddc98b76aaab1cdb13e2665353cd2f","tid":2350192,"uid":303858,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f9b3db73bc015963d1fc482fec3e21f8d406e706","tid":2350192,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"聽首歌都要分<br />\n你聽埋我果份啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"原來聽歌不應涉及政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"當首歌走撚哂音，唔講政治，講佢個撚樣呀？"},{"pid":"bead15410433c38f071bb758192d5b8a809f33af","tid":2350192,"uid":127972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"講真，就算唔講政治，都唔會值至尊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得純粹係商台想佢嚟表演make noise的等價交換"},{"pid":"9f837db8e080f5be15799fd01b3c1e0cfa3be703","tid":2350192,"uid":34738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"首先唔講佢唱歌唱好似粵曲咁撚樣，首先首歌我完全唔識欣賞，最撚大鑊啲歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />填詞條撚樣係咪食撚大左先填，咩床邊有你廳有你進出於腦海、咩寧願閉氣吸進你、乜柒野詞黎架想點撚樣啊⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ea26439cbc50340606a2b1174f3886e018139b","tid":2350192,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f837db8e080f5be15799fd01b